Just because something sucks doesn't mean it's not true.Don't you see the foolishness in believing in something simply because you want it to be true?And the blind man analogy doesn't work because the blind man could verify the existence of the color blue through rational thought. Science tells us in detail about how the eye and the brain work together to perceive colors. It tells us nothing about God.